quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Tõnd tʋmsa a Nuuh a nebã nengẽ, n tɩ yeel-bɑ: ""bugs f nebã taoor tɩ naong sẽn zabd nan pa wa-b ye""."
  71,2,"T'a yeele: ""yaa yãmb m nebã, ad mam yaa bugsd sẽn vẽneg ne yãmba""."
  71,3,"Tɩ y tũ Wẽnde, la y zoe-A la y tũ maam."
  71,4,"A yaafda yãmb n yi y zunuub-rãmba, la A yaool-y n tʋg wakat sẽn yãk raare. Wẽnd raarã sã n wa, pa yaoond ye, yãmb sa n da miime""."
  71,5,"T'a yeele: ""m Soaba! Mam boola m nebã yʋng la wĩndga."
  71,6,"La mam baoolã pa paas-b sã n pa zoees bal ye!"
  71,7,"La ad maam, mam sẽn bool-b tɩ Fo na yaaf-b fãa, b ningda b nus-bi wã b tʋbẽ wã, la b pil b futã n kell n nangdẽ la b waoogd b mense, waoogr tεkẽ."
  71,8,"Rẽ poorẽ, ad mam bool-b-la vẽeneg-vẽenega."
  71,9,"Rẽ poorẽ, mam vẽneg n wilg-b lame, la m leb n solg n wilg-b solgr tεkẽ."
  71,10,"Tɩ m yeele: kos-y yaafa ne y Soabã, ad Yẽnda yɩɩme n yaa yaafa Naaba."
  71,11,"A tʋmsda saagã yãmb nengẽ t'a kiigdẽ."
  71,12,"La A leb n paas yãmb arzεk la koamba, la A maan pʋt n kõ yãmba, la A leb n maan n kõ yãmb sẽn yaa ko-soodo."
  71,13,"Yaa bõe n tar yãmb tɩ yãmb pa tɑr rɑbeem ne Wẽnd zɩslmã?"
  71,14,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka A naana yãmb naaneg sẽn pʋg taaba."
  71,15,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmb pa ne to-to ning Wẽnd sẽn naan saas a yopoe n fõg taaba?"
  71,16,"La A maan kiuugã a pʋgẽ tɩ yaa nuura, la A maan wĩndgã tɩ yaa vẽenem."
  71,17,"La Wẽnd n buls yãmb n yi Tẽngã, bulsg tεkẽ."
  71,18,"Rẽndã poorẽ A lebsda yãmb a pʋgẽ, la A leb n yiis yãmb ne yiisgu."
  71,19,"Lɑ Wẽnd n maan Tẽngã n kõ yãmb tɩ yaa sẽn yεdge."
  71,20,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ y paam n tuk a zug soay sẽn yalme."
  71,21,"A Nuuh yeelame: ""m Soaba! b kɩɩsa maam la b tũ ned ning arzεk la a biig sẽn pa paasd-ɑ sã n pa bõn bala."
  71,22,"La b rabs rabr sẽn yaa bedre."
  71,23,"La b yeele: ra tol n bas-y yãmb soaben-dãmbã ye, ra n bas-y-yã a Wad la a Sʋwa-a la a Yagʋʋs la Ya-ʋʋk, la a Nasr ye!"""
  71,24,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka b menemsa neb wʋsgo, la F ra paas wẽgdbã sã n pa menengo."
  71,25,"B tʋʋm-beedã yĩnga, b bõr-b lame n kẽes-b Bugmẽ; b pa paam sõngdb sã n pa Wẽnd ye."
  71,26,"La a Nuuh leb n yeelame, ""m Soaba! Ra bas Tẽng poor zug kɩfr-dãmbã ned ba a yembr ye."
  71,27,"Ad Foo, F sã n bas-ba, b menemesda F yembsã; b pa rogd me tɩ sã n pa wẽngdã n yaa kɩfre."
  71,28,"M Soaba! yaaf-ma, la m roagdb a yiibã, la ned fãa sẽn kẽ mam zakã t'a yaa sɩd-kõtɑ, la sɩd-kõatbã fãa, la sɩd-kõat-posgsã fãa. Lɑ ra paas wẽngdbã ralla halkre""."
